  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31513781">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63379397/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63379397-6.jpg" alt="一期一会" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31513781/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31513781/" class="">第23页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63379397/" class=" " title="一期一会">一期一会</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31513781">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有财富的社会，如果在心灵的层次上还没有提高到对人的关爱，还没有扩及到对弱者的包容，它也是一个落后的社会。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-07 15:23</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>有财富的社会，如果在心灵的层次上还没有提高到对人的关爱，还没有扩及到对弱者的包容，它也是一个落后的社会。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

